{"title":"烈士塑像","authors":["赵启顺"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":10,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士塑像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵启顺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从战火中走上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族骨骼凝固的底座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起硝烟中的形象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们没有把你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安放在金碧辉煌的殿宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让你伟大在天穹下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相伴你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有垂柳、雪松、鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们在为你短暂的死"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换取永恒的生而礼拜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在为你擎起红星擎起真理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擎起民族的尊严而致敬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你选定的绿色事业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我心中是山峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是历史，是昨天的教训"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是今天，是魄力和未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的脚印写出的道路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我眼睛里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是太阳金丝织出的光带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传送着金色齿轮和麦穗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"护卫五颗灿烂星座的赞歌"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}